{"tid":793649,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"為什麼要從 iOS 轉到 Android？","createTime":"2018-08-25T14:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T17:05:10.000Z","uid":109383,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1981987e3b700f8001757344a5d64fd8bcf9db","tid":793649,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"PCMag 近日對 2500 位美國消費者進行了一次更換手機 OS 調查，了解人們為什麼要從 iOS 換到 Android 以及從 Android 換到 iOS。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不足 3 成用戶會轉 OS<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n調查所見，只有 3 成用戶會考慮轉 Mobile OS，當中 iOS 轉 Android 的有 11%，而從 Android 轉到 iOS 則有 18％。<br />\n<br />\n換 OS 換因為更佳使用體驗？<br />\n<br />\n問及換 OS 的原因，iOS 轉 Android 或是 Android 轉 iOS 也說是為了更佳的使用體驗，而從 Android 轉 iOS 的人更有 47% 是因為此原因而轉。相對 iOS 轉到 Android 的用戶，當中只有 30%。不過從 iOS 轉到 Android 的用戶中，第 2 個主要功能是因為價格相宜，此原因佔了 29%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/switchos01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Fswitchos01.jpg&h=93f87370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半數人等壞了才換新機<br />\n<br />\n不過有趣的是 56% 受訪者表示他們不太關心新手機發佈，而有 34% 用戶表示他們會在電訊公司合約完時才會換手機，更有一半人表示他們只會在電話壞掉才會換機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論 無錢先用android an狗年年換機係因為壞機被迫換<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377a5c357912a63b2f17475a999b04ea6061ee29","tid":793649,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:00:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e996e34d1a5e75f34cae25c6a3cb265fd0bedf2","tid":793649,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:02:41.000Z","msg":"成功挑起紛爭老師會加幾多分？"},{"pid":"0fa5da93dc85612e1488f2a7e2ddfea180b57078","tid":793649,"uid":164092,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:03:47.000Z","msg":"Smart Octopus<br />\n快無線叉<br />\nMST<br />\nBlack Theme<br />\nDual Apps<br />\nDual Sim<br />\nDobly Atoms<br />\nAlways On Display<br />\nKnox<br />\n無M字